    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the CFD hemolysis predictions for the VAD COU and determined that the Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification results demonstrate sufficient confidence in the model predictions. The hemolysis index predictions fall below the ASTM F1841 clinical threshold across all five operating points. The team accepted the model for regulatory submission based on the overall simulation evidence package, noting that further work on unassessed factors is recommended for the next assessment cycle.",
